I"F<h1 class="post-title" itemprop="name headline">Binding Pockets</h1>
<p>This page shows some of the comparisons of the binding pockets from different riboswitches. We sorted out three comparisons, ‚ÄòPurine riboswitches family‚Äô, ‚ÄòSAM riboswitches family‚Äô, and ‚ÄòGuanidine riboswitches family‚Äô as shown in the following figures.
<br />
<br /></p>

